SUMMARY:Nature Book Club
DESCRIPTION:Join Lorrimer Sanctuary for our book discussions on all thing’s nature. Nature Book Club meets the 4th Tuesday of the month to read books focused on nature topics. Books are usually found through BCCLs on Hoopla or Libby. All are welcome! \nIf you are interested in getting updates about the books we are reading\, join our book club email list by contacting Alexa: Alexa.Fantacone@njaudubon.org. \nCOST: FREE \nMEETING LOCATION: NJ Audubon’s Lorrimer Sanctuary\, 790 Ewing Ave\, Franklin Lakes\, NJ 07417 \nCLICK THE FOLLOWING FACEBOOK LINK TO JOIN THE DISCUSSION: Nature Book Club – Facebook \n 
