UID:10010660-1774706400-1774710000@njaudubon.org
SUMMARY:Rainbow Roundup Nature Walk
DESCRIPTION:Spring has sprung! All around us\, the colors of the rainbow are popping up in nature! Can you collect them all? During our Rainbow Roundup Nature Walk\, we will take a gentle stroll around the Nature Center of Cape May trails in search of all the colors of spring. We will identify the first blooms of the season\, search for signs of wildlife\, and collect a few natural treasures along the way. Can you find all the colors of the rainbow? This program is best suited for children 10 and younger. Kids under 2 are free. \nImportant note: This is not a drop-off program; adults must accompany children. Participation is limited. Pre-registration is required. \nCOST: Children $8\, Adults $12 \nIMPORTANT INFORMATION:  We may walk up to a mile\, over generally level surfaces. Some surfaces may be muddy or uneven. Please dress warmly and wear sturdy footwear. \nWHERE: Nature Center of Cape May (1600 Delaware Ave\, Cape May\, NJ 08204) \nWHEN: Saturday\, March 28\, 2 pm-3 pm \n\n\nCANCELLATION POLICY: NJ Audubon’s programs require a minimum number of registrants to run. If we cancel\, due to lack of participation\, severe weather\, or unforeseen circumstances\, all participants will be notified as soon as possible and are eligible for a full refund. Participants may cancel without penalty if greater than 48 hours in advance. Sorry\, no refund for cancellations less than 48 hours in advance unless due to health emergencies; however\, registrations can be transferred to another program in the future. \n\n\nREGISTER HERE
URL:https://njaudubon.org/event/rainbow-roundup-nature-walk/
LOCATION:Nature Center of Cape May\, 1600 Delaware Avenue\, Cape May\, NJ\, 08204\, United States
CATEGORIES:Event,Family Program,Nature Center of Cape May,Nature Walk
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://njaudubon.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/Rainbow-Roundup-Nature-Walk.jpg
GEO:38.9452704878;-74.8992712451
